{"tid":2259276,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【好嬲好嬲】法國13個區將出版諷刺伊斯蘭漫畫併發給高中生","createTime":"2020-10-26T16:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T02:00:22.000Z","uid":29188,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1fbbde4f89683514e6c4639daacac0900e9698","tid":2259276,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>塞繆爾&middot;帕蒂遇刺案：一本漫畫書即將在高中發行</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.en24news.com/24/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/caricature-charlie-hebdo-illustration-8cc684-0@1x.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.en24news.com%2F24%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fcaricature-charlie-hebdo-illustration-8cc684-0%401x.jpeg&h=075a8d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國的13個地區將出版一本關於政治和宗教諷刺漫畫的書籍，以回應薩繆爾&middot;帕蒂（Samuel Paty）老師被暗殺的情況在高中發行。法國大區地區主席雷諾&middot;穆塞里爾（Renaud Muselier）週一在會議上宣佈了這一決議，該會議將塞納-聖但尼的聖瓦恩社區聚集在一起。<br />\n<br />\n「我們是法國各地區的主席，現在正在積極準備出版一本書，該書將地區出版社出版的最傑出的宗教和政治諷刺漫畫與國家出版社出版的那些漫畫匯集在一起。」雷諾&middot;穆塞里爾（Renaud Muselier）被判犯了這樣的「卑鄙而怯懦的暗殺」，他補充說：「我們將要求歷史專家來解釋諷刺漫畫對於我國政治史的重要性。」<br />\n<br />\n後者規定，國家教育部將「<em>與這項倡議聯繫起來，以便可以向法國的所有高中學生提供這本書</em>」「<em>以這種姿態，在尊重我們的技能的同時，我們希望證明我們捍衛共和國的價值觀以及我們每一位同胞的和平與自由生活的基本權利的承諾。</em>」法國地區主席強調。<br />\n<br />\n法國城市長協會主席Fran&ccedil;ois Baroin為此表示歡迎，該代表「是向法國所有高中大規模傳播自由的一種表達，同時也要求『共和秩序』在全國領土上建立」。LCI於本週二早上與該組織聯繫，諾曼底地區主席埃爾維&middot;莫林（Herv&eacute; Morin）以此表示歡迎：「只要它也具有其他宗教的諷刺意味，我就支持它。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.en24news.com/2020/10/assassination-of-samuel-paty-a-book-of-caricatures-soon-to-be-distributed-in-high-schools.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.en24news.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fassassination-of-samuel-paty-a-book-of-caricatures-soon-to-be-distributed-in-high-schools.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETSWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=30373074\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.en24news.com/2020/10/assassination-of-samuel-paty-a-book-of-caricatures-soon-to-be-distributed-in-high-schools.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6df48cf7da2723bde75ea8715518750f4f402f9","tid":2259276,"uid":121146,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"連法膠都覺醒  美膠居然想走返回頭路？"},{"pid":"4377a8b9d692e0819056dc92d8a3ab402fc20b39","tid":2259276,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"支持右翼抬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a9386d4fa57f3779a76bae4c5614bf4417943f","tid":2259276,"uid":58320,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n融入唔到就返鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82626a25537dc1dca7da57c111b7533affb122be","tid":2259276,"uid":324629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4377a8b9d692e0819056dc92d8a3ab402fc20b39","tid":2259276,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"支持右翼抬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"睇嚟今次係右翼vs左膠之戰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9eba78e8d27298fed857d1de44f6c4e499b959","tid":2259276,"uid":40267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b6df48cf7da2723bde75ea8715518750f4f402f9","tid":2259276,"uid":121146,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"連法膠都覺醒  美膠居然想走返回頭路？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"法國不嬲右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0be410f370f7ba4c764393e647167982ae8fbd6","tid":2259276,"uid":266676,"lik